%% API Client-Server Communication Model
%% File: api_client_server.mmd
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client<br/>(Browser/Mobile/CLI)
    participant A as API Server<br/>(Application Layer)
    participant D as Database<br/>(Data Layer)

    C->>A: 1. HTTP Request<br/>(Method + URL + Headers + Body)
    activate A
    A->>D: 2. Query / Command
    activate D
    D-->>A: 3. Data / Result
    deactivate D
    A-->>C: 4. HTTP Response<br/>(Status Code + Headers + Body)
    deactivate A

    Note over C,D: Stateless: Mỗi request độc lập,<br/>server không lưu session
